This was created by Aiden Pawelko. Feel free to make edits!

Each key does something. Each example:
  - W makes it go forward
  - A makes it go to the left
  - S makes it go backward
  - D makes it gp to the right
  - Q makes it look left
  - E makes it look left
  - R makes it go up
  - F makes it go down
  - K makes it increase speed
  - L makes it decrease speed
  - Z makes it land
  - X emergency stop
